{"tid":425865,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[助攻] 三星手機喺衫袋發熱爆炸 男子拎出「火球」灼傷胸","createTime":"2017-10-06T05:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T09:01:10.000Z","uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe8e43efcd3aac7b68cc0538d7925ed4f1585a0","tid":425865,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57293629&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57293629%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171006&d=Vw%2BPPaDukkvmVNujyjkxCBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=8f80d336\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57293629%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171006&h=859df899\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57293629&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171006</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171005/large/1507192231_52ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171005%2Flarge%2F1507192231_52ae.jpg&h=21cabcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼一名酒店主管工作期間，放在胸口口袋的三星手機突然發熱爆炸，手機頓成火球，幸他立即脫去上衣，僅胸口有少許燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發在三寶瓏（Semarang）一間酒店，從影片看到47歲主管尤利安托(Yulianto)在大堂與其他人閒聊之際，突然他用手查看胸口口袋位置，口袋隨即爆炸發出閃光着火有如一個小火球，他大吃一驚跌倒地上，然後立即脫去著火的上衣。旁人見狀也上前協助。<br />\n<br />\n尤利安托指自2013年起就使用這部三星Grand Duos手機，一直沒有問題，當時手機同時開啟Wifi、藍芽和GPS，相信爆炸因過熱引起，「我強烈感到一股熱力，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有東西在震動</span></span>，在知道發生甚麼事前已經着火，我很慌張，立即盡快除下上衣」。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，幸而尤利安托盡快脫去衣服，因此減輕了受傷程度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/mobile-phone-explodes-mans-pocket-11287565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-news%2Fmobile-phone-explodes-mans-pocket-11287565&d=Vw%2BPPaDukkvmVNujyjkxCBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=4afd0755\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/mobile-phone-explodes-mans-pocket-11287565</a> 助攻片段"},{"pid":"0ff7b3ff69f4d05590700b17aee3f9b6cfd30a49","tid":425865,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815df247626d256c5a1c3f74387bb108ae90bb26","tid":425865,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"三星:真多工 真爆炸"},{"pid":"0ab01d93a6186b335f3091b1b152a233f69c9112","tid":425865,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"2013年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f11a44b567599f80837c1009405f34f72bb8a4","tid":425865,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/140514_7c9d06022365309a8a1b254a85660c67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F140514_7c9d06022365309a8a1b254a85660c67.jpg&h=8ef9a415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔識野果啲唔該收聲！"},{"pid":"e8879909ea1e69dd40781562d5bce333f5d01cee","tid":425865,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"十大武器之首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16eb210aa3e6dbcb50d425c78cb86426d637b34f","tid":425865,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.gundam.info/uploads/image/thumbnail/20130422194016-27894.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.gundam.info%2Fuploads%2Fimage%2Fthumbnail%2F20130422194016-27894.jpg&h=4d9c9046&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d89c795e9961da38ee8d641f023b30ecfdb46ede","tid":425865,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:01:10.000Z","msg":"唔明點解仲有人用三叔 雖然話係舊機<br />\n但都係完全失去信心"}]}